--button-shadow-focus.light:
inset 0px 1px 0px 0px #ffffff, inset 0px 0px 0px 1px #000000,
    inset 0px calc(var(--button-inset-shadow-size) * -1) 0px 2px #000000,
    inset 0px -2px 4px 0px #000000, 0px 4px 4px -5.6px #000000,
    0px 2px 4px -2.7px #000000, 0px 2px 4px -1px #000000,
    0px 0px 0px 3px var(--color-l-alpha-gray)

--button-accent-shadow-focus.light:
inset 0px 1px 0px 0px #ffffff, inset 0px 0px 0px 1px #000000,
    inset 0px calc(var(--button-inset-shadow-size) * -1) 0px 2px #000000,
    inset 0px -2px 4px 0px #000000, 0px 4px 4px -5.6px #000000,
    0px 2px 4px -2.7px #000000, 0px 2px 6px -1px #000000,
    0px 0px 0px 3px var(--color-l-alpha-gray)

--underline-decoration-color.light:
color-mix(
    in srgb,
    currentColor var(--underline-decoration-opacity),
    transparent
  )

--link-ahref-decoration-color.light:
color-mix(
    in srgb,
    currentColor var(--link-decoration-opacity),
    transparent
  )
